.gitignore
# …but the MkDocs source IS needed by the docsbuild stage (mkdocs build).
# These negations re-include it in the build context (it's excluded above via
# `docs/` and `*.md`). mkdocs.yml is not ignored, but listed here for clarity.
!mkdocs.yml
!docs/
!docs/**
